{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01K2aH6LWMLE5XteXU6ozLfW","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_019okvzdcmZWe9xm7mKN6mTU","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/200-visual-regression/history.md","old_string":"## Iteration 5 — 2026-02-18T14:07:59Z — OK\n- **Log**: iteration-005.log","new_string":"## Iteration 5 — 2026-02-18T14:07:59Z — OK\n- **Log**: iteration-005.log\n\n## Iteration 6\n**Item**: Create shared test fixture in `apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts`\n**Result**: ✅ Success\n**Notes**: Created `apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts` with a `stablePage` fixture that extends Playwright's `test`. The fixture: (a) injects CSS to disable all animations/transitions/scroll-behavior via `!important` rules on `*, *::before, *::after`, (b) wraps `page.goto()` to use `waitUntil: \"networkidle\"`, re-inject animation CSS after navigation, and `await document.fonts.ready`, (c) adds a 200ms settle time for remaining paints. Exports `test` and `expect` for use in visual test files. `npx playwright test --list` parses without errors. Lint passes (0 errors)."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":417,"cache_read_input_tokens":69730,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":417},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fa292fd5-d07e-4e2d-9d66-18303d0ed43d","uuid":"9fb89290-32b7-4c2c-a77a-cb73808c1ab9"}
